These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, cabbage
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | coffee  | sprite |
| Food       | pumpkin | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | fanta |
| Sport      | swimming     | lacrosse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, crime
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, russian
1. the polish is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the polish is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | crime  |
| Nationality   | polish | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, radish
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk   |
| Food       | radish | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, punk
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, british
1. the british is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | country    |
| Nationality   | canadian | british |

