.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
2 different pets are kept: fish, hamster
1. the polish is on the left or right of the german##3
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | german | polish |
| Pet           | hamster     | fish  |

