The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby   | traveling   | camping |
| Sport   | basketball | badminton   |

 